38:55.709 --> 38:56.698
(GIGGLES)

38:56.793 --> 38:58.624
Hey.

38:58.712 --> 39:01.419
This is our
little secret,
right?

39:03.759 --> 39:05.795
All right.

39:06.011 --> 39:10.254
I know it's scary at first,
