39:32.079 --> 39:33.535
MOHlNDER: Monica Dawson?

39:33.622 --> 39:34.702
Yes.

39:34.790 --> 39:38.328
l'm Dr. Mohinder Suresh.
May I?

39:41.129 --> 39:42.665
Can I help you?

39:42.756 --> 39:45.964
I'm sure you have lots
of questions about
what's happening to you.

39:48.095 --> 39:50.131
Well, I have some answers.

39:53.976 --> 39:55.011
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

39:55.102 --> 39:56.933
