39:58.230 --> 40:02.314
Hi. Yup. I'm fine.
Weather could be better.

40:03.652 --> 40:05.859
No. Not yet. lwill.

40:06.488 --> 40:08.524
He's here.

40:09.116 --> 40:11.607
Had to improvise
a little, but...

40:12.536 --> 40:17.280
No, I mean
ljust had to use
a little persuasion.

40:17.374 --> 40:19.410
That's all.

40:22.796 --> 40:24.878
No. It was just some guy,

40:26.091 --> 40:28.127
and l...

40:28.302 --> 40:31.510
All right, I killed him, okay?
