40:33.473 --> 40:35.759
What do you mean? Now?

40:38.979 --> 40:42.062
This is my assignment,
and I almost have him.

40:45.902 --> 40:48.029
What if I promise not to...

40:49.615 --> 40:51.446
Fine.

40:51.533 --> 40:53.569
I'll come home now.

40:55.203 --> 40:56.454
(ENGINE STARTING)

40:56.538 --> 41:00.122
Sorry, Daddy,
it won't happen again.

41:19.394 --> 41:20.804
(EXHALES)

41:24.733 --> 41:26.223
What happened?

41:26.318 --> 41:27.854
I don't know.

41:28.528 --> 41:31.270
Apparently you're
a genius of
an artist, too.

41:31.365 --> 41:33.697
I painted that? How?

41:33.784 --> 41:35.900
How do you shoot lightning
from your hands?

41:36.036 --> 41:39.870
All I know is
your eyes went dead,
and you couldn't be stopped.

41:40.248 --> 41:42.580
Until there was this.

41:42.668 --> 41:43.657
Is that us?

41:43.752 --> 41:45.162
PETER: I don't know. Maybe.

41:45.253 --> 41:46.834
What do you think this is?

41:46.922 --> 41:48.458
CAITLIN: A Church?

41:48.548 --> 41:50.880
The street signs
are in French.

41:52.594 --> 41:55.506
Could be Montreal.
Like the plane ticket.

41:56.223 --> 41:58.054
